Description: Metron Technology is an independent supplier of fab-wide support services to the semiconductor and related industries.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: Outsourcing is the emerging trend in today's semiconductor industry. Dramatic swings in the global business environment have companies re-evaluating costly, inflexible business practices and adopting outsourcing as a preferred alternative. The purest form of outsourcing in the semiconductor industry was introduced with the concept of the foundry. Many chip manufacturers embraced that foundry outsourcing model and repositioned themselves as "fabless", however no options existed for companies to outsource other, non-core functions - until now. Metron is exclusively focused on bringing revolutionary outsourcing alternatives to the semiconductor industry. Since 1975 Metron has steadily developed the expertise and resources needed to serve semiconductor industry customers at all levels of technology and in all parts of the world. With unrivaled services and products and an infrastructure that spans Asia-Pacific, Europe and North America, Metron provides the only global outsource solution in the industry today. Semiconductor manufacturers are able to streamline their supply chain by outsourcing through Metron. By offering Fab Solutions for outsourcing critical non-core functions, Metron enables its customers to better focus valuable resources on developing competitive technologies. Equipment manufacturers are able concentrate on the development of new generation equipment and maintain critical levels of support for mature equipment with Metron Equipment Solutions. Metron's focus on early generation equipment ensures customer satisfaction through an extended product life cycle. Suppliers gain access to a global market by leveraging Metron's Fab Solutions and Equipment Solutions. Metron manages the rapid, cost-effective introduction of products while suppliers can concentrate on core product development and manufacturing competencies. Working with its supplier and equipment manufacturer allies has allowed Metron to offer solutions that truly complement semiconductor manufacturers' prime mission - making superior product. Streamlining the supply chain has also allowed Metron customers to cut costs and adapt more quickly to changing global markets. Those key value propositions drive The Outsourcing Solutions Company.

Description: Modern point of sale and inventory management software for the cannabis industry
Full Description: LeafOps is a web-based, seed to sale, point of sale, and dispensary management software solution for modern cannabis dispensaries. We remove the hassles of state traceability systems and state regulations so that dispensaries can focus on running a retail business at its core. LeafOps deeply integrates with state traceability systems like Leaf Data Systems, and Metrc so that inventory and sales can be automatically reported in the background as sales are made.  In addition to a suite of retail features such as loyalty programs, flexible and rule-base discounts and a user-friendly cash register interface, LeafOps keeps dispensaries in compliance by providing tools such as ID checks, purchase limiting, and other state-specific compliance features that are essential in the cannabis industry. At it's core, LeafOps was built on a foundation of reliability, where every customer gets their own database (backed up and encrypted daily), load balanced and auto-scaled server instances, and a proven infrastructure that scales to meet the demands of the most successful 4/20 sales day.
